data.description: Discover your dream home in this stunning cul-de-sac property, located in the highly desirable lake community of Stratland Estates. This meticulously maintained residence boasts an inviting open floor plan, perfect for entertaining family and friends. The heart of the home is the modern kitchen with high-end appliances and a center island, overlooking the spacious living area. Step outside to your own private oasis - a beautiful pool and outdoor space, ideal for relaxing and hosting poolside gatherings. With numerous upgrades both inside and out- including a 4ft extended garage, this home offers both style and functionality, making it a true gem in the market. **Over $50k in upgrades completed between 2016-2023
